{#
  Home page — GOV.UK "Start now" pattern.

  This is the first page a user sees. It explains the service and
  provides a prominent green "Start now" button to begin the journey.

  In the real Rural Payments portal, the user would sign in via
  Defra Identity first. This demo skips authentication to focus
  on the embedded screen pattern.
#}
{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% from "govuk/components/button/macro.njk" import govukButton %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">{{ pageTitle }}</h1>

      <p class="govuk-body-l">
        Use this service to view and manage your farming business information,
        including BPS entitlements, applications, and land use.
      </p>

      <p class="govuk-body">
        This is a demonstration of how the Single Front Door (SFD) service
        embeds Siti Agri screens within its pages using iframes and an SSO bridge.
      </p>

      <div class="govuk-inset-text">
        In the real service, you would sign in with your Rural Payments
        account via Defra Identity before accessing business information.
        This demo skips authentication to focus on the embedded screen pattern.
      </div>

      {{ govukButton({
        text: "Start now",
        href: "/business",
        isStartButton: true
      }) }}
    </div>
  </div>
{% endblock %}
